
Use linear system 
xdot=Ax+Bw w+Bu u 
y=Cx+Dw w+Du u +n

xhatdot=Axhat+Bu u+L(y-yhat)
yhat=Cxhat+Du u

edot=Ax+Bw w+Bu u-Axhat-Bu u-L(y-yhat)
    =Ax+Bw w+Bu u-Axhat-Bu u-L(Cx+Dw w+Du u-Cxhat-Du u)
    =(A-LC)e+(Bw-LDw)w+Ln

with suitable L, Bw-LDw=0
edot=(A-LC)e+Ln


Pi (y-Du u)=Pi Cx+Pi Dw w+Pi n
           =Pi Dw w+Pi n

Piw (y-Du u)=Piw Cx+Piw Dw w+Piw n
            =Piw Cx+Piw n

